<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>דשבורד בעל המכולת</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
    <style>
      .dashboard-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .dashboard-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #26a69a;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 16px;
        text-align: center;
        min-width: 180px;
      }

      .dashboard-button:hover {
        background-color: #1e867c;
      }

      .logout-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 40px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>ברוך הבא, בעל המכולת!</h1>
    <p>בחר פעולה:</p>

    <div class="dashboard-container">
      <a href="/owner/order" class="dashboard-button">הזמנת סחורה מספק</a>
      <a href="/owner/orders" class="dashboard-button">צפייה בסטטוס הזמנות</a>
    </div>

    <div class="logout-container">
      <a href="/" class="dashboard-button">התנתק</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
